# 10 Secure Development and CI Gates

## Intent
Make privacy and security controls enforceable in daily engineering workflow.

## CI Platform
- GitHub Actions is the required CI system for the rewrite product.

## Mandatory
- CI must run secrets scanning, dependency scanning, and static analysis.
- Enforce tests for consent checks, access controls, and deletion/export workflows.
- Block merges/releases when critical compliance gates fail.
- Maintain patch/vulnerability remediation SLAs by severity.

## Tooling Rules
- Add lint/test checks preventing raw personal data logging.
- Include schema/policy validation for data classification and retention tags.

## Prohibited
- Manual gate bypass without documented emergency approval.
